2015;;Chorus;;Canadian;;François Delisle;;Sébastien Ricard, Fanny Mallette, Geneviève Bujold, Pierre Curzi;;drama;;https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Chorus_(2015_film);;One afternoon, Hugo, son of Christophe and Irene disappeared, and the life of the married couple would shatter. After 8 years, the searches found nothing, as the two got a divorce, and lived their own lives apart, with Christophe moving to Mexico.[3]